ploinMailFactory

  The ploinMailFactory (in the past "javaMailFactory") is a mailing framework that provides extended
  features like a templating mechanism, multitenancy and localizaion.
  Internally it uses the commons-email API from Apache.


* Features

  * 83% code coverage with JUnit 4.4 and Clover2
  
  * Templating system for e-mails

  * Multi-client capability

  * Internationalization

  * Load balancing for e-mail server

  * Fall back server definition

  * Retry function

  * Defining delay time between the retrys

  * Very small footprint, 29 kb.